 'FAILURE TO REGISTER: Manafort, Rick Gates, and others failed to register under the Foreign Agents Registration Act (FARA) while lobbying in the U.S. for Ukrainian interests. They created the "European Centre for a Modern Ukraine "as a front group.',
 'RUSSIAN INTELLIGENCE CONTACT: The Treasury Department designated Konstantin Kilimnik, Manafort\'s longtime Ukrainian associate, as a Russian intelligence officer. Manafort shared internal Trump campaign polling data with Kilimnik.',
